<v-app-bar
  app
  color="primary"
  dark
>
  <v-img
    class="logo"
    @click="onDashboard"
    src="/images/logo.png"
    max-width="130"
    contain
  />

  <v-btn
    color="primary"
    class="toolbar-btn"
    @click="onDashboard"
  >
    {{ $t('mindloggerDashboard') }}
  </v-btn>
  <v-btn
    color="primary"
    class="toolbar-btn"
    @click="onLibrarySearch"
  >
    {{ $t('mindloggerLibrary') }}
  </v-btn>
  <v-spacer />
  <v-btn
    v-if="isLoggedIn"
    class="toolbar-btn"
    color="primary"
    @click="onLogout"
  >
    {{ $t('logout') }}
  </v-btn>
  <v-btn
    v-else
    color="primary"
    class="toolbar-btn"
    @click="onLogin"
  >
    {{ $t('login') }}
  </v-btn>
</v-app-bar>
